[Body]
== Description ==
Neurons application

The "src_blanks" folder contains the Neurons application with blanks.
Only for tutorial purposes.


== Execution instructions ==
Usage:
runcompss --lang=python src/neurons.py 128 <size> <spikesFile>

where:
		 * - size: Size
		 * - spikesFile: Absolute path to the spikes file


== Execution Examples ==
runcompss --lang=python src/neurons.py 128 $(pwd)/data/spikes.dat
runcompss src/neurons.py 128 $(pwd)/data/spikes.dat
python -m pycompss src/neurons.py 128 $(pwd)/data/spikes.dat

== Build ==
No build is required
